527
00:32:07,220 --> 00:32:08,400
Smile.

528
00:32:08,400 --> 00:32:10,320
Show me your smile.

529
00:32:15,960 --> 00:32:17,960
Xinxin, you're here too.

530
00:32:17,960 --> 00:32:19,660
Where's our gorgeous new neighbor?

531
00:32:19,660 --> 00:32:21,019
