551
00:33:07,839 --> 00:33:09,599
I'll help you unpack.

552
00:33:09,599 --> 00:33:11,500
Okay.

553
00:33:11,500 --> 00:33:13,820
Na Na told me you're a pro at making beds. Can you teach me?

554
00:33:13,820 --> 00:33:15,099
All right, I'll make your bed.

555
00:33:15,099 --> 00:33:18,339
Okay. I'll dig in.

556
00:33:20,520 --> 00:33:22,600
You're leaving?

557
00:33:22,600 --> 00:33:26,200
I already told A'Yao. I won't be volunteering here these days.

558
00:33:26,200 --> 00:33:27,620
I'll take a couple of days off.

559
00:33:27,620 --> 00:33:31,540
Y-You... Will you come back?

560
00:33:31,540 --> 00:33:34,880
Yes. I'll definitely come back to visit you.

561
00:33:34,880 --> 00:33:37,680
