570
00:34:11,900 --> 00:34:15,119
These will do for now. If she wants more, we'll send her more.

571
00:34:15,119 --> 00:34:17,700
That's true.

572
00:34:17,700 --> 00:34:24,280
Xiaochun told me that Hongdou's lease is ending, and she hasn't renewed it.

573
00:34:24,280 --> 00:34:27,639
Yeah. She's going back to find a job.

574
00:34:27,639 --> 00:34:31,420
What's going on between the two of you?

575
00:34:31,420 --> 00:34:35,280
Hold on. So, is no one willing to believe our refutations of that rumor?

576
00:34:35,280 --> 00:34:37,360
If that's what you're saying,

577
00:34:37,360 --> 00:34:41,959
I'll get Xiaochun to find more people for your blind dates.

578
00:34:42,480 --> 00:34:44,760
Look at me. Do I have time for a relationship?

579
00:34:44,760 --> 00:34:49,739
Girls don't have time for relationships, either. They all date while working.

580
00:34:50,500 --> 00:34:53,520
Someone is wooing Xiaochun.

581
00:34:54,780 --> 00:34:55,799
